🎥👨🏾‍🎓👩🏽‍🎓WATCH: Many grads in a historically black college, Bethune Cookman-University, booed and turned their backs to Trump's Secretary of Education Betsy Devos during her commencement speech. The students told me they didn't think she had any business speaking here today and that it was important for them to take a stand using the hashtag #BacksToBetsy. 'We are making a difference,' one said, 'it's a big deal'. The school stood by their decision. Here's our story on @msnbc #Reporting #ItMatters #golikemariana .
